string 
    strip:  remove prefix and post fix
    rstrip: only remove the post fix

    judge if empty/blank string: 
        if s.strip(): 


numpy
    ravel()
        like flatten, but no copy
    
    where(Cond, A, B) 
        make a array from A or B according to Cond

    slice() and reshape() all will create a view, no copy

commandline arguments
	import argparser
	
	parser = argparser.ArgumentParser()
	parser.add_argument("--show_shape", action="store_true", help="show the shape of parameters")
	args = parser.parse_args()

	main(args.show_shape)
